CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe International Energy Agency warns
OL,8,Fthat the blockade of the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz, through which around 20% of
OL,10,Fthe world's oil usually passes, will
OL,11,Fmean less supply, as ITV News
OL,12,FEconomics Editor Joel Hills explains
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, the boss of the world's
OL,15,Flargest oil company, Aramco, warned of
OL,16,F"catastrophic consequences" if the war
OL,17,Fdrags on.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FBut the following day, the chancellor
OL,8,Fwas asked what support she might offer
OL,9,Fbusinesses and households already
OL,10,Ffeeling the strain, not least when
OL,11,Ffilling up the car.
OL,13,F"Nothing is off the table," she told
OL,14,FMPs.
OL,16,FThe reason energy prices are rising is
OL,17,Fsimple. The Strait of Hormuz - one of
OL,18,Fthe most important oil routes on the
OL,19,Fplanet - remains effectively closed.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FOn a normal day, almost 200 oil and
OL,8,Fgas tankers pass through the narrow
OL,9,Fshipping lane between Iran and the
OL,10,FUnited Arab Emirates. It is the choke
OL,11,Fpoint through which a significant
OL,12,Fshare of the world's energy supply
OL,13,Fflows.
OL,15,FBut on Wednesday, for a tenth
OL,16,Fconsecutive day, barely anything moved.
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, barely any ships moved
OL,19,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz according
OL,20,Fto this tracker by Marine Traffic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FWhen that happens, the effects cascade
OL,8,Fquickly through the energy system.
OL,9,FCountries in the Gulf cannot export.
OL,10,FStorage facilities start filling up.
OL,11,FAnd eventually production itself has
OL,12,Fto be cut.
OL,14,FThat is why the International Energy
OL,15,FAgency has agreed to release 400
OL,16,Fmillion barrels of emergency oil
OL,17,Fstocks.
OL,19,FAt first glance, that sounds enormous.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FIn reality, it represents roughly a
OL,8,Fmonth's worth of oil flows that would
OL,9,Fnormally pass through the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz.
OL,12,FAnd even that oil will not arrive
OL,13,Finstantly. It is still unclear which
OL,14,Fcountries will release what, and how
OL,15,Fquickly those barrels will actually
OL,16,Freach the market.
OL,18,FSome analysts say the scale of the
OL,19,Frelease suggests governments are
OL,20,Fpreparing for a prolonged disruption
OL,21,Frather than a short shock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the ripple effects are
OL,8,Falready spreading through the global
OL,9,Feconomy.
OL,11,FThe price of jet fuel has jumped by
OL,12,Faround 50% in the past week. If that
OL,13,Fincrease persists, airlines will
OL,14,Feventually pass the cost on to
OL,15,Fpassengers through higher ticket
OL,16,Fprices.
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump has promised
OL,19,Fmilitary escorts for tankers and even
OL,20,Finsurance guarantees to encourage
OL,21,Fships back into the Gulf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FBut for now, shipping companies still
OL,8,Fsee the area as too dangerous to enter.
OL,10,FReleasing emergency oil stocks may
OL,11,Fhelp contain the surge in energy
OL,12,Fprices.
OL,14,FBut it does not solve the underlying
OL,15,Fproblem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773425169
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FUntil tankers can safely pass through
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz again, the
OL,9,Fworld's energy system will remain
OL,10,Funder strain, and 400 million barrels
OL,11,Fof oil will not be enough to end the
OL,12,Fcrisis.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
